## AmpMod manual and dev docs
The AmpMod manual and developer documentation are hosted on Codeberg.
See their [privacy policy](https://codeberg.org/codeberg/org/src/PrivacyPolicy.md).

## Source code
The source code of all AmpMod software is hosted on Codeberg.
See their [privacy policy](https://codeberg.org/codeberg/org/src/PrivacyPolicy.md).